data.description:
Discover timeless comfort in this ranch-style residence located in the heart of Belpre, Ohio. This home offers an invitation to infuse your personal style into three bedrooms and two full baths, complemented by a fully finished basement that awaits your creative touch for entertainment or leisure.

Upstairs beneath the current carpeting lies a hidden treasure of original wood flooring, offering a wonderful opportunity to reveal a classic and elegant touch to the home. The property features a level backyard with a storage shed for all your outdoor essentials, as well as a garage equipped with cabinets and shelving, not to mention the added convenience of a carport. Two welcoming gas fireplaces anchor the upstairs and downstairs living spaces, setting the stage for cozy evenings and cherished memories.

In this home, you'll find abundant space and storage to cater to all your needs, along with a canvas for bringing your modern vision to life. This is a home for those looking to blend classic charm with their own design dreams, in a neighborhood that speaks home in the community of Belpre. Embrace the opportunity to craft your ideal living experience in a setting that promises the ease of one-level living.
